description: T.p. vignette with port. of Monti. Seven full-page engraved ill. included in paging; that on p. [11] is after Riccardo Taurino. Numerous in-text emblems, & ports. in the form of depictions of sculptured busts; many signed by Giovanni Paolo Bianchi as engraver. Signatures: a b A-O PÂ². Binding: later vellum, painted red. Tooled in gilt with frame and central ornament. Two holes for ties at foredge. Property stamps of Jan Borms on back pastedown
